{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/AboutBannerEvilAwaits_.png?t=1733660667\" />After receiving a distress call about an explosion, a detective travels to the remote Archdale Castle in search of answers but finds herself trapped. Can you find out what happened? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/Evil_Awaits_General_Banner.gif?t=1733660667\" /><strong>Find Notes, Solve Puzzles, and Use Key Items</strong> to progress through haunting <strong>Atmospheric Environments</strong> in this indie <strong>Action Survival Horror</strong>. Use a range of <strong>Firearms, defensive options and Melee Strikes</strong> to take on the horrors that await and <strong>Learn Movement Techniques</strong> &amp; <strong>Upgrade Equipment</strong> that suit your playstyle to prepare for <strong>Intense Boss Battles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/FeaturesBannerEvilAwaits_.png?t=1733660667\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Range of terrifying environments -</strong> From the open sea of the misty docks to the tight crypts of a haunted cemetery. Evil Awaits has a range of terrifyingly atmospheric and realistic environments filled with collectables, keys, puzzles, notes, encounters and surprises.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/PillarGIFCropped1.gif?t=1733660667\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Face a diverse horde -</strong> A variety of mutations stand between you and what awaits, all with different move sets &amp; weaknesses. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/Evil_Awaits_Combat_Banner.gif?t=1733660667\" /> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Refine your loadout -</strong> A range of melee attacks, defensive options, firearms, and more can be found throughout the Archdale grounds. Everything upgradeable from toolkits you will find along the way. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/Evil_Awaits_Upgrades_Banner.gif?t=1733660667\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cinematic -</strong> Evil Awaits hosts a range of suspenseful cinematic in-game cutscenes, one of many aspects that tell the tale of the Archdale family curse.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/Evil_Awaits_Cinematic_Banner.gif?t=1733660667\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Horror in your control -</strong> An adapted control scheme allows for swapping sides as well as third &amp; first-person aiming. More 'classic' perspectives are to be added in the future.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survive -</strong> A variety of Brutal boss encounters and dangerous hazards lie in wait, can you overcome the challenge?</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Explosive Toll","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2194930/616a0632af8771818fa6893450fa6dbfcc316ec9.jpg"},{"name":"The Gardeners Solitude","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2194930/c9784423e021470db33236f6dd58ceff0be28d58.jpg"},{"name":"By Land Or Sea","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2194930/5b3879881196d403ce85b1521c6bbcf76c2f253b.jpg"},{"name":"Megadrile Massacre","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2194930/89c9a08cb700ff908e12ad98bdd40aff02d8698c.jpg"},{"name":"Leviathan Challenge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.ste